{"tid":805532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華演唱會門票10時開售　9時許已無法登入城市售票網","createTime":"2018-09-04T01:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T05:54:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d9a7061b726af0375c704f676e1ebc1df73fc8","tid":805532,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:52:11.000Z","msg":"劉德華將於12月在紅館舉行跨年演唱會，日前發生門票尚未開售，但歌迷排隊輪候時遭人斬傷事件，劉德華宣布煞停售票處公開售票，只設網上、流動應用程式及信用卡電話訂購，今早10時開售。《明報》記者今早9時許已無法由上述3個途徑登入城市售票網。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180904/s00001/1536024511402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180904%2Fs00001%2F1536024511402&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=585b41f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180904%2Fs00001%2F1536024511402&h=26b971ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180904/s00001/1536024511402</a>"},{"pid":"390983bc4c9c6b5335ef3b0d985b2d12457aa2e3","tid":805532,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573f036916ce82a482f8b29427b6ffe59425da34","tid":805532,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"老豆都冇飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！boom! 比雷劈！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c267e00db27b8051163e242d6c01660d5db28125","tid":805532,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"573f036916ce82a482f8b29427b6ffe59425da34","tid":805532,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"老豆都冇飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！boom! 比雷劈！<img